VariCAD Viewer is a free viewer, convertor and printing software working
with 2D DWG, DXF, 3D STEP and 2D/3D VariCAD file formats. VariCAD viewer
allows you to convert DWG to DXF and vice-versa, convert STEP to 3D IGES
or STL formats, print 2D DWG, DXF or VariCAD formats and use batch print
or batch conversions. All conversions are also available between VariCAD
native format and other listed formats. VariCAD viewer offers settings of
3D display methods (like light source or perspective). 3D display can be
also exported into high-resolution bitmap file.

WWW: https://www.varicad.com/
